import React from "react";
import { Grid, Box, Input, InputLabel } from "@material-ui/core";

export default function MemberInput() {
  return (
    <>
      <Grid container spacing={1}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Box>
            <InputLabel>asd</InputLabel>
            <Input
              type="text"
              className="member-input form-control  shadow-none"
              placeholder="Customize your Personal Invite Code"
            />
            <Box className="form-text color-orange font-ubun">
              PLEASE NOTE: Once you save the code, it can't be changed later, so
              please make sure it's what you want
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </>
  );
}
